text: Dichostates biflavoplagiatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lepesme and Breuning in 1952.BioLib.cz - Dichostates biflavoplagiatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1952
